{"tid":217253,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"1個鐘內 由幾百負評變成正評反超","createTime":"2017-04-25T16:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T12:34:38.000Z","uid":42246,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ea1dd77cee299c761af62a8748ed5bb0ea12917","tid":217253,"uid":42246,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:01:17.000Z","msg":"唔講刪post單野 只講刪post正負評問題<br />\n有留意既巴打 應該睇到一直都係負評多幾百票<br />\n<br />\nPost入邊重有人叫比負評既人死返去高登<br />\n但係約11點 唔知係咪道德撚集體放工<br />\n每分鐘幾十正評咁上 一個鐘反超負評<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想問 咁樣大家覺得正常？<br />\n想話我高登打手既 起一起我個底先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ba4fcc9adbfc0ccb478df2c886f6edb608eebe","tid":217253,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:03:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/26/000354_720ccc46475fa55d1d1bce567a6c9b69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F26%2F000354_720ccc46475fa55d1d1bce567a6c9b69.jpg&h=69d4c657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60f7aacd8e4fb4a683f70dabefcd31d6c7156d59","tid":217253,"uid":54574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"收錢收到心雄仲點會畀你班契弟搞事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6221f0b48ab622baea59d2afee27edbae4220366","tid":217253,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T16:10:15.000Z","msg":"連仔原post<br />\n<br />\n#257 2h前<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">希望負評嘅各位真係返高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢度唔啱你 走啦</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我一入去睇就係見到依句<br />\n重回覆左個位巴打 連投票結果都接受唔到 <br />\n少數個一方先應該離開連登去高登<br />\n<br />\n個時負評多正評2xx票 <br />\n<br />\n大家覺得正常？"},{"pid":"07a775