\n<br />\nOk 你話呢種屈人post會毀人地清白<br />\n咁前幾日牛角AA制單野 初初一出新聞時個個話係個女要個男人請 個個話佢臭雞 又盛<br />\n哦 呢d又叫有證據 唔會傷害到人既 <br />\n到前日個老細出黎講返件事 <br />\n有無del返哂呢d所謂無證無據 傷害他人清白既post?<br />\n<br />\n係咪屈人 自己識諗架啦 <br />\n<br />\n大佬呀 我上高登 到後黎連登都係想食花生咋嘛<br />\n睇人仆街 不嬲都係咁架啦 <br />\n做乜攪到正義撚上身咁呀"},{"pid":"342ad07680b7e078931e7d1313144a5e1a402d44","tid":217253,"uid":66253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"64ee3e811dfbdceb6bf75e2d2c8c6c4c2ee8f2a5","tid":217253,"uid":27391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:36:58.000Z","msg":"正負皮被反超都賴到做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8614a39d6d27472c0b3a74f830a05c2ffae9c03b","tid":217253,"uid":21514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"第一次開post負評多過正評<br />\n仲唔做野咩"},{"pid":"b27c6864dad37b73ca419ae9ed3a91bfd759a165","tid":217253,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:59:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正負皮被反超都賴到做假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以夜晚十一點道德撚真係集體放工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一個鐘300正評 你都覺得正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原本一直負評多幾百票"}]}